---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="How Not To Diet - Weekly Menu Planner">
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Weekly Menu Planner</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Evidence-based nutrition planning for optimal health</p>
  </div>

  <section class="intro">
    <h2>Welcome to Your Food Science-Based Menu Planner</h2>
    <p>
      Plan your weekly meals using principles from evidence-based nutrition science.
      This tool helps you create balanced, nutritious menus that align with the latest
      research on healthy eating.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3><a href="/foods">Food Database</a></h3>
        <p>Explore 10+ foods with synergies, timing, amounts, and source pages from "How Not to Diet"</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Anti-inflammatory foods</li>
          <li>High fiber & low glycemic</li>
          <li>Daily Dozen & 21 Tweaks</li>
          <li>Tagged with chapter names</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3><a href="/combos">Food Synergies</a></h3>
        <p>Discover powerful food combinations that maximize health benefits</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Top triple combos for meals</li>
          <li>Scientifically-backed pairs</li>
          <li>Quick meal ideas</li>
          <li>Synergy score rankings</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3><a href="/planner">Weekly Planner</a></h3>
        <p>AI-generated weekly meal plan optimizing food synergies</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Complete 7-day plan</li>
          <li>Daily Dozen coverage</li>
          <li>21 Tweaks integration</li>
          <li>Shopping list ready</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="data-source">
    <h2>Data Source</h2>
    <p><strong>Book:</strong> "The How Not to Diet Cookbook" by Michael Greger, MD</p>
    <p><strong>Extracted:</strong> 10 foods with complete synergy data, timing recommendations, and source page tracking</p>
    <p><strong>Coverage:</strong> Anti-inflammatory foods, fiber-rich, low-glycemic, chronobiology principles, Daily Dozen, and 21 Tweaks</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 0;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .intro {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .intro p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .features {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card h3 a {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .feature-card h3 a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .feature-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card ul li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: #555;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .feature-card ul li::before {
    content: "âœ“";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .data-source {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .data-source h2 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .data-source p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .feature-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
